At 7 ranks, the character can try to purge their body of disease when they use Second Wind. <PRO_HISHER> chance of success is 35% plus <PRO_HISHER> Constitution modifier.

This ability cannot be used in combat.

Effect: Heals 25% of target's max hit points, +10% per rank, plus Constitution Modifier.

Chance of Success: 
Poison (6 ranks) 10% per rank + Constitution Modifier.
